title: See the Fisher-Price® On-the-Go Baby Dome in action! |  Fisher-Price
description: Whether you’re at home, visiting the grandparents, or enjoying a family trip to the beach, with the Fisher-Price® On-the-Go Baby Dome, your little cuddle bug can stay cozy and entertained no matter where you are! This portable play space has everything your baby needs to nap, play, or enjoy some tummy time. And with its fold-flat design and handles, it’s super easy to grab and go.
